<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>A Special Note for Friends</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Netflix jaisa subtle grain effect */
        .netflix-bg {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1a1a 0%, #000000 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-black text-zinc-300 font-sans selection:bg-red-600 selection:text-white">

    <!-- Main Container with Netflix Radial Gradient -->
    <div class="netflix-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6 relative overflow-hidden">

        <!-- Decorative Red Glow (Netflix Theme) -->
        <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-red-900/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-red-900/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>

        <div class="relative max-w-3xl w-full z-10" data-aos="fade-up">

            <!-- Header Section -->
            <header class="mb-12 border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-6">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter uppercase">
                    A Special <span class="text-red-600">Note</span> 
                </h1>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 font-medium mt-2 tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">For my best friends</p>
            </header>

            <!-- Message Section -->
            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium text-zinc-300 text-left " data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="3000" >

                <p
                    class="first-letter:text-5xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:text-red-600 first-letter:mr-3 first-letter:float-left">
                    Aaj 11/03/26 10pm baithe-baite purani baatein yaad aa rahi thi ya soch rha tha  ki meri Tum sab mere liye kya ho  !. Sach bataun , meri puri life mein mujhe tum jaise dost pehle
                    kabhi nahi mile.  Jab bhi me purani baton ko yaad karta hoon, toh samajh aata hai ki college mere liye sirf
                    padhai ya degree ka zariya nahi tha, balki  tum jaise yaaron ko paana tha.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Hum college mein mile zaroor hain, lekin tumne itne kam waqt mein mere dil mein jo jagah banayi hai,
                    woh shayad bachpan ke Friend bhi nahi bana paate. Meri life ke har mod par, tum sab ne meri help
                    ki—chahe wo exams ka stress ho, meri personal pareshaniyan, ya wo chhoti-chhoti khushiyan—tumne
                    hamesha mera Saath diya hai.
                </p>

                <p class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 italic shadow-2xl">
                    "I really don’t want us to be just 'college friends.' I want this friendship to last way beyond these four years."
                </p>

                <p>
                    "Thanks for being there through everything. Means a lot."
                </p>

            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800 flex justify-between items-center">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Hamesha saath rehna! Bruhh...</p>
                    <p class="text-white font-black text-2xl tracking-tight"> >>> </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="h-12 w-12 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 font-bold">
                    A.K
                </div>
            </footer>

            <div class="mt-12 text-centre">
            <a href="/home2">
                <button class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold tracking-wide transition duration-300 shadow-lg hover:scale-105">FlashBack   </button>
            </a>
        </div>

        </div>
        
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({
            duration: 2500, // Global speed
            once: false
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>